      • recognize

        public VisualRecognitionImages recognize(File image)
        Classifies the images against all the label groups and labels. The response includes a score for a label if the score meets the minimum threshold of 0.5. If no score meets the threshold for an image, no labels are returned.
        Parameters:
        image - the image file
        Returns:
        the visual recognition images

      • recognize

        public VisualRecognitionImages recognize(File image,
                                         LabelSet labelSet)
        Classifies the images against the label groups and labels. The response includes a score for a label if the score meets the minimum threshold of 0.5. If no score meets the threshold for an image, no labels are returned.
        Parameters:
        image - the file image
        labelSet - the labels to classify against
        Returns:
        the visual recognition images
